### 🔷 2. The $3 Trillion Developer Economy

- **30 million** professional software developers globally
- Average economic value: **$100,000/year**
- Total: **$3 trillion developer economy** being restructured in real time

**Why software disruption is unique — "Software Disrupts Software":**

| Other Industries | Software |
|---|---|
| Agriculture disrupted by tractors (external) | Software is disrupted by software (internal) |
| Farmers could adapt gradually over decades | No "adapt gradually" option — tools, workflow, mental models shift simultaneously |
| SaaS solved deployment problem | AI agents solve the **intelligence problem** |

> SaaS: "pay for tools" → Agent Era: **"pay for outcomes"**

