- Web (1995–2005): early learners became leaders
- Mobile (2008–2015): iOS dev in 2009 had massive advantage over 2012
- Cloud (2010–2018): early AWS engineers shaped the era
- **AI-Native: we are at Year 1–2 RIGHT NOW (2026)** — window is open but closing fast

